 the software and services segment provides wide are network controller network functions virtualization platform and software applications the company was founded by patrick h nettles in november  and is headquartered in hanover md valuation pe current  pe ratio with extraordinary items  pe ratio without extraordinary items  price to sales ratio  price to book ratio  price to cash flow ratio  enterprise value to ebitda  enterprise value to sales  total debt to enterprise value  efficiency revenueemployee  income per employee  receivables turnover  total asset turnover  liquidity current ratio  quick ratio  cash ratio  profitability gross margin  operating margin  pretax margin  net margin  return on assets  return on equity  return on total capital  return on invested capital  capital structure total debt to total equity  total debt to total capital  total debt to total assets  longterm debt to equity  longterm debt to total capital  officers and executives name age officer since title dr patrick h nettles   executive chairman mr gary b smith   president chief executive officer  director mr james e moylan   chief financial officer  senior vice president mr stephen b alexander   chief technology officer  senior vice president mr james a frodsham   chief strategy officer  senior vice president insider actions – purchase – sale  – number of transactions  no credit card required already a subscriber sign in ciena  a network strategy and technology company  ciena network insights products and services support and next steps explore insights thanks to our people and our customers for making ciena a great place to work and one of the worlds most admired companies insights by topic softwarebased transformation endtoend packet networking redefining optical networks data center interconnect more article geomesh extreme release the kraken ciena’s brian lavallée delves into the depths of submarine networks and their importance to global communications and how ciena’s new geomesh extreme allows submarine cable operators to integrate several technology advancements to enable an open submarine network solution with greater choice and performance insights for your enterprise finance utilities media  entertainment more explore products and services thanks to our people and our customers for making ciena a great place to work and one of the worlds most admired companies converged packet optical packet networking  family  more more liquid spectrum wavelogic ai sdnnfv management software blue planet blue planet manage control and plan visit more services services for your network more all products list the ciena community explore next steps thanks to our people and our customers for making ciena a great place to work and one of the worlds most admired companies contact sales email toll free  international     more see all offices get support support by phone support portal join the ciena community view our partners meet up at an event subscribe to the network insights general inquiries  more thanks to our people and our customers for making ciena a great place to work and one of the worlds most admired companies about us newsroom partners investors careers worldwide support can we help you answer a question can we help you answer a question sure im good thanks are you a current ciena customer yes no not sure do you need support on an existing product yes no were happy to help visit our community contact support do you want to learn more about cienas products yes no heres some useful information connect with ciena learn more about us do you want to learn more about cienas products yes no do you need support on an existing product yes no heres some useful information connect with ciena learn more about us thanks to our people and our customers for making ciena a great place to work and one of the worlds most admired companies skip the beach geomesh extreme delivers directly to your data center learn more have questions we have answers chalk talk g